 
<p>
One thing we can  expect in last stages before total disaster is that people
will <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/news/2022/07/25/climate-catastrophe-feared-congo-moves-sell-critical-ecosystem-oil-drilling">desperately pollute and destroy unusual ecosystems</a>, to delay the local
disaster a few more years.  Now the DR Congo is about to open up a large
rainforest for oil drilling.

 